<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16152] Solr Standalone: bin/solr package fails with NullPointerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16152</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Basic standalone installation as service on rocky linux&lt;br/&gt;
Package Manager is not usable&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;bin/solr package list-available&lt;/b&gt; fails with &lt;b&gt;NullPointerException: Cannot invoke &quot;String.indexOf(int)&quot; because &quot;connectString&quot; is null&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


